law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts. ch. 24, sec. 1079, effective July 15, 2010; and repealed 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 83, sec. 21, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 194, sec. 2, effective July 14, 2000.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Licensing of specialty credit insurance producers -- Authorization of employees or representatives -- Rights and limitations.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2010). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 83 prevails over its amendment in 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24.
